{"type": "article", "id": 26479, "title": "爆米花包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-06T07:08:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130808zUkYtqpASJgNhnbH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">西班牙的 <a href=\"http://tatabistudio.com/\">TATABI Studio</a> 最近为 Diz-Diz 微波炉爆米花设计的包装选择了高端奢侈路线，颠覆了大众对这一零食的认识。干酪、咖喱、肉桂和香草四种口味以不同金属色的包装分装，外包装的纸盒则印刷上了大理石纹，折叠之后还能用来盛爆米花，既时尚又实用。对爆米花爱好者们而言，可能又带来了另一种（甜蜜的）烦恼：因为太好看即便买回家也舍不得吃。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130806Q9BugUqZDrk51OhM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130806PnJ4HZB0p6tgbQsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130807k8yFPnJrQ59bjEqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130807UxgeT4f38kh0OMnc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}